| archive = Box 7. Charles Edward Russell Papers, Manuscript Division, Library of Congress, Washington, DC
| date = June 17, 1917
| url = 
| doi =}}</ref>
Wilson was receptive and the CPI subsequently developed film and distribution networks in Russia over the next few months. 
