=== Film ===
Russell played himself in the 1917 film ''[[The Fall of the Romanovs|The Fall of the Romanoffs]]'', a dramatization of the Russian revolution and the influence of Rasputin on the Russian royal family.<ref>{{IMDb title |0007927 |The Fall of the Romanoffs}}</ref>

